Class ModelMessage<Payload extends Serializable>

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.messages.ModelMessage<Payload>
Type Parameters:
Payload - Generic Payload parameter, must be Serializable.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AvailableLobbyMessage, BoardMessage, CommonGoalMessage, CurrentPlayerMessage, EndGameMessage, IncomingChatMessage, ServerResponseMessage, ShelfMessage, StartGameMessage, UpdateScoreMessage
public abstract class ModelMessage<Payload extends Serializable> extends Object implements Serializable
MVC model messages parent class.
Every message that originate from the model must inherit from this class.
Every Message class should define its own payload class.
For details consult the network manual.
